# and project-level metadata (*.md).
* @GoogleCloudPlatform/nexus-sdv-core-maintainers

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Infrastructure & Deployment (IaC)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Responsible for Terraform, GCP Cloud Build, ARM64, and Orchestration logic.
